  "text": "Instead of the recursive enumeration used in many previous algorithms [CITATION_1] - [CITATION_2] , we use iterative enumeration. By using Johnson-Trotter permutation algorithm [CITATION_3] and Gray code, each enumeration step only swap one pair of adjacent symmetric classes, or flip one symmetric class. Thus the transformation cost during enumeration is minimized.",
